definitions.definition: A town , port , and civil parish with a town council in south-west Cornwall , England ( OS grid ref SW8132 ) .
A village in Hants County , Nova Scotia , Canada .
A number  of places in the United States :

subdefinitions.definition: An unincorporated community in Suwannee County , Florida .
An unincorporated community in Fairview Township, Fayette County and Union Township and Washington Township, Rush County , Indiana .
A city , the county seat of Pendleton County , Kentucky .
A town and census-designated place therein, in Cumberland County , Maine .
A town and census-designated place therein, in Barnstable County , Massachusetts .
An unincorporated community and census-designated place in Clam Union Township, Missaukee County , Michigan .
A census-designated place in Conoy Township, Lancaster County , Pennsylvania .
A census-designated place in Stafford County , Virginia .

definitions.definition: A port town in Saint Paul parish, Antigua , Antigua and Barbuda .
A town , the parish capital of Trelawny parish, Jamaica ; named for the harbour town in Cornwall , England .
A rural community of Break O'Day council area, Tasmania , Australia .
